ncy<br>of the entire team\'s recovery skills, and increases<br>their energy levels.<\/div><div class=\\"skill-detail\\">Recovery Potency: 72<br>Skill Energy Required: 4,819<br>Special Effects:<br>\\u30fbRecovery Potency +10%<br>\\u3000\\u3000Lasts 10 seconds<br>\\u30fbEnergy Level +1<br>\\u3000\\u3000Charges: 1<br><\/div><\/dd><\/dl><\/div>\\n\\t<div class=\\"exAbility explanation\\">\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Co-ability<\/div>\\n\\t\\t<dl>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/799d30d618475a89802dad3d29b6ca252.png\\"><\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Recovery Potency +20%<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dd>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tIncreases the potency of recovery skills by 20%.<br>Benefits your whole team.\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dd>\\n\\t\\t<\/dl>\\n\\t<\/div>\\n\\n\\t<div class=\\"exAbility explanation\\">\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Chain Co-ability<\/div>\\n\\t\\t<dl>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/87595b7438e74e5502d8b830d6bd16832.png\\"><\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>(Light) Energy = Strength +9%<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dd>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tIf a team member is attuned to Light: <br>increases their strength by 9% for 15 seconds<br>when their energy level is increased.<br>After activating, this ability will not<br>activate again for 15 seconds.<br>Benefits your whole team.\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dd>\\n\\t\\t<\/dl>\\n\\t<\/div>\\n<div class=\\"ability explanation\\">\\n\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Abilities<\/div>\\n\\t<dl><dt><span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/7fbb4902dda7202f798ff5244afce94a2.png\\"><\/span><span>Mighty Crescendo<\/span><\/dt><dd><div>Increases the potency of recovery skills by 15%.<br><br>Using Spirited Song grants the user the<br>\\"Dispel Strike\\" effect. When this effect is active,<br>the user\'s next force strike will dispel one<br>enemy buff. This effect cannot stack and will<br>be consumed on use.<br><br>Also, using Agitato Assault will grant the user a<br>strength amp with a maximum team amp level<br>of two. After this amp is granted, this ability<br>will not grant it again for 30 seconds.<\/div><\/dd><dt><span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/4dc1a81f441225fffc1959459d81bfb62.png\\"><\/span><span>Vigorous Conducting<\/span><\/dt><dd><div>Reduces susceptibility to sleep and poison<br>by 100%. When the user is hit by an attack that<br>would have put them to sleep or poisoned them,<br>their strength is increased by 15% for 10 seconds.<br>This increase will not stack, and, after activating,<br>this buff cannot be activated again by the same<br>affliction for 15 seconds.<\/div><\/dd><dt><span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/24dc1983d110ed627df93dd3e6322d962.png\\"><\/span><span>Skill Prep +100% & Skill Charge<\/span><\/dt><dd><div>Fills 100% of skill gauges at the start of quests.<br>Using a skill fills skill gauges by 5%.<\/div><\/dd><\/dl><\/div><\/div><\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Notes:<\/div><div>1. The stats shown here represent the adventurer at level 100 with 70 mana nodes unbound.<\/div><div>2. The stats shown here do not include increases or decreases due to abilities.<\/div><div>3. The stats for the adventurer included in this notification shown in any prior notifications or preview videos were the stats at level 80 with 50 mana nodes unbound.<\/div><div>4. When an adventurer&#39;s skill level increases, the skill gauge will fill more slowly when set as a shared skill.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.<\/div>","start_time":1627970400,"prev_article_id":"2352","next_article_id":"2389","image_path":"","update_time":1627628926}}}'